trans-unit.source: Represents an OLE compound file that contains an encrypted package.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en sammansatt OLE-fil som innehåller ett krypterade paket.

trans-unit.source: EncryptedPackageEnvelope has no public constructors.
trans-unit.target: EncryptedPackageEnvelope har inga offentliga konstruktorer.

trans-unit.source: An EncryptedPackageEnvelope is created by use of the static <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope.Create%2A>, <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope.CreateFromPackage%2A>, or <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope.Open%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: En EncryptedPackageEnvelope har skapats med hjälp av statiskhet <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope.Create%2A>, <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope.CreateFromPackage%2A>, eller <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope.Open%2A>metoder.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope.Open%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope.CreateFromPackage%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope.Create%2A>

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Frigör alla resurser som används av den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when finished with a <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>.
trans-unit.target: Anropa Dispose när du är klar med <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Dispose lämnar den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>oanvändbar.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: När du anropar Dispose, måste du släppa alla referenser till den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>så skräpinsamlingen kan frigöra minne som den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>var upptar.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [Rensa ohanterade resurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) och [implementera en metod för ta bort](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid anropet avyttra innan du släpper senaste referens till <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope> object's <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: De resurser som den använder frigörs annars inte förrän skräpinsamlingen anrop av <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>objektets <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metod.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Släpper de ohanterade resurser som används av den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope"> </xref> och släpper du de hantera resurserna.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose()`method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden anropas av allmänheten `Dispose()`metod och <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metod.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`anropar den skyddade `Dispose(Boolean)` metod med den `disposing` parametern `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>anropar `Dispose` med `disposing` inställd på `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is true, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope> references.
trans-unit.target: När den `disposing` parametern är true, den här metoden Frigör alla resurser som innehas av alla hanterade objekt som den här <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>referenser.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden startar den `Dispose()` metod för varje refererade till objekt.

trans-unit.source: Gets the core package properties (such as Title and Subject) of the rights managed document.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar grundläggande Paketegenskaper (till exempel rubrik och ämne) rättigheter hanterat dokument.

trans-unit.source: These core properties are stored in the standard OLE property streams (\005SummaryInformation and \005DocumentSummaryInformation).
trans-unit.target: Dessa huvudegenskaper lagras i standard OLE-egenskapen strömmar (\005SummaryInformation och \005DocumentSummaryInformation).

trans-unit.source: The core properties are also stored in the package itself.
trans-unit.target: Core egenskaperna lagras också i själva paketet.

trans-unit.source: It is the responsibility of the application to keep the two sets of properties synchronized.
trans-unit.target: Ansvarar för att hålla två uppsättningar med egenskaper som synkroniseras.
